title: Mama Cass Elliot - Self-Titled CD - Japanese Release - FLAC
description:
Mama Cass Elliot - Self-Titled CD - Japanese Release - FLAC


Japanese only re-release. All 10 original tracks included. Tracks, 'I'll Be Home', 'Baby I'm Yours', 'That Song', 'Wh en It Doesn't Work', 'I'll Be There', 'I Think It's Gonn a Rain Today', 'It's All In The Game & More', 'Jesus Was A Crossmaker' & 'Disney Girls'. Includes lyrics to all tracks, Originally released in 1971 on the Buddha label. Standard jewel case.

These songs are already available via the "Rarities" torrent, but those versions were ripped from the original vinyl LP album and had some popping and background noise.    The present torrent is ripped via EAC directly from the rare Japanese CD release instead.
